'''Steamcrawlers''' were large tracked vehicles used by the [[Balawai]] on [[Haruun Kal/Legends|Haruun Kal]], especially in [[jup]]s. They were equipped with [[Turret/Legends|turrets]] and large [[Lamp/Legends|headlamps]]. They were purposefully low tech so that they could better resist the metal-eating [[Fungus/Legends|fungus]] of Haruun Kal. They were the basis of the [[Ground assault vehicle/Legends|Ground Assault Vehicle]].

